data.name: label2.Text
data.value: IN A GRIPPING TALE, CYBER CHALLENGE, THE VALIANT DEFENDER OF THE DIGITAL WORLD, FACES AN UNEXPECTED PROBLEM AS HE FORGETS HOW TO CREATE A STRONG PASSWORD. WITH CYBER VILLAINS CLOSING IN, HE MUST EMBARK ON A JOURNEY TO REDISCOVER THIS VITAL SKILL AND REINFORCE HIS VIRTUAL FORTRESS BEFORE IT'S TOO LATE.
